August 6, 2004 | Professor Miller talks about his book, Cruel and Unusual: Bush/Cheney’s New World Order, published by W.W. Norton and Company. Mr. Miller argues that the Bush administration is leading the country to a place where democracy will be the thing of the past. The author compares President Bush’s leadership to that of ruthless dictators. After the discussion, Mr. Miller answers questions from members of the audience. 

